data.description: Welcome home to this charming 2 bedroom 1 bathroom home in Olmsted Falls. This is a great condo alternative for those who don't want an HOA. Well maintained and updated this home is a must see! This spacious kitchen has room for all your cooking needs, with two adjacent rooms you have options to set up your ideal house flow. Both of these rooms have wood floors for an additional welcoming feel. The large backyard is full of green space to create your own outdoor oasis. Located less than a mile from downtown Olmsted Falls. This home is ready for its new owners!
